Package presentation

Interface Summary
PresentationElement Interface for any element that can be displayed in the drawing area.
 

Class Summary
CubicParamCurve2D A cubic parametric curve segment defined by float coordinates and having extended capabilities: parameter-specified subdivision and computation of bounds on curve length.
Geometry A set of operations on 2D points and vectors including rotation, translation, subtraction, scaling, taking the norm and dot product of vectors and finding the midpoint of a cubic curve.
GraphicalLayout Encapsulates the basic position and appearance characteristics of graphical elements displayed in the graph views.
QuadTreeNode TODO Implement for optimization of intersection in FSMGraphModel.
